lenders.name: Raymond
lenders.loan_because: it's the right thing to do!
lenders.occupational_info: I myself am in the process of rebuilding my life, having gone from a success to a complete collapse. Having had it all and then experienced the loss of everything, I can really identify with these people's plight. Every little bit helps and in helping others we help ourselves in the process... it's our responsibility as compassionate souls to make a difference to other people's lives where we can and this site is an excellent channel to do this, I am grateful I was introduced to it. I know I will get back up again and It makes me happy to help others in need along the way.
